        "info": "\n      <h1>King James Version, American Edition</h1>\n      <p>King James Version 1611, spelling, punctuation and text formatting modernized by ABS in 1962; typesetting &#169; 2010 American Bible Society.</p>\n      <p>If you are interested in obtaining a printed copy, please visit the American Bible Society at <a href=\"http://www.bibles.com/\">www.bibles.com</a>.</p>\n    \n    \n    ",
